title: Problem & Jahlil Beats - Fastest Record To Radio
description:
Unlike anything done in hip-hop before, we combined the talents of super
producer Jahlil Beats with rapper Problem to complete what can only be
called "the fastest record to radio." Assembling at Victory Lane Studios
in Los Angeles, watch the process as two songs go from the early stages of
completion to a finished product - which is then delivered to the LA
Leakers at Power 106 and played for the world to hear.
